data.name: Blackwing - Oroshi the Squall
data.desc: If you control a "Blackwing" monster other than "Blackwing - Oroshi the Squall", you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). You can only Special Summon "Blackwing - Oroshi the Squall" once per turn this way. If this card is sent to the GY as a Synchro Material: You can target 1 monster on the field; change that target's battle position.

card_sets.set_name: Dragons of Legend: The Complete Series
